9088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 170}, {\"ngram\": \"Zverev\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-final stage\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles competition\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It probably would not have counted for much, givenNovak Djokovicappeared to be on a one-man mission to take home gold.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"givenNovak\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-man mission\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in the wake of last week's Olympic tennis meet, Zverev has blasted the organisers of the Games.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"last week's Olympic tennis meet\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"Zverev\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our community members\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"special offers\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"promotions\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Speaking to the Tennis Channel, Zverev said: \\\"I preferred Tokyo because I prefer to win gold, of course, but it's always special to be in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tennis Channel\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_Channel\"}, {\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.984961823747289, \"rank\": 0.010663118994852297, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"Zverev\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This year it was strange because it was in Roland Garros, a place we all know very well.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999984877863491, \"rank\": 1.5118539018049964e-06, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the same time, it was very different.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Village wasn't the best, I have to say.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Village\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed there, the whole German team stayed there, our federation wanted it.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9952631964710611, \"rank\": 0.004683317946865135, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our federation\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We suffered a little because of food, we suffered a little from sleeping conditions.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"sleeping conditions\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was no air conditioning in the rooms either, which was a bit difficult for me but it was the same for everyone so I do not complain.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the rooms\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lack of air conditioning was picked up on by the Team GB chiefs in the build-up to the Games, with the rooms housing British athletes having been retro-fitted with AC units.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9865940687647077, \"rank\": 0.012309600118188624, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/