985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zverev is yet to win a Grand Slam, having last come close at the French Open earlier in the summer.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zverev\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"a Grand Slam\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Open\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy The 27-year-old was brushed aside in the final byCarlos Alcaraz, with Zverev admitting he's still hurting from the defeat: \\\"We are both physically strong but he's a beast, he's an animal for sure and the intensity that he plays tennis is different to that of other people.\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.742501809072213e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q39